data.title: Strength of My Life by Vertical Worship
data.meta_description: Original Master MultiTracks, Charts, Patches, and instrument parts for rehearsal. View all products & resources available for "Strength of My Life" by Vertical Worship
data.text:
Verse 1

Let the weak say I am strong

Faith is rising

Mountains fall away

You are always holding on to me

Chorus

You are the strength of my life

You flood the darkness with light

I throw myself on Your never failing love

You are the strength of my heart

I'm running into Your arms

I throw myself on Your never failing love

Verse 2

I will walk and not grow faint

Through the valley

You will make a way

You are always holding onto me

Chorus

You are the strength of my life

You flood the darkness with light

I throw myself on Your never failing love

You are the strength of my heart

I'm running into Your arms

I throw myself on Your never failing love

Bridge

Almighty Savior

You are the anchor for my soul

Your name is greater

Greater than any other name I know

Chorus

You are the strength of my life

You flood the darkness with light

I throw myself on Your never failing love

You are the strength of my heart

I'm running into Your arms

I throw myself on Your never failing love
